At 41%, your client is grabbing files from the patching server. When you see crashes or errors here, it usually means that the connection to the patching servers dropped off. This can be caused by some incompatible network settings locally, or in rarer cases, issues with your route to that server. In either case, it's a good idea to check your network settings and ensure they're aligned with our [connection guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if this helped.
